{"author":"Iso Tester","data":{"body":"Implemented + BLOCK remediated: revised ticket to the achievable design (advisory native-opengrep rules, deny-by-default exposure signal, engine_b lang fix) and re-ran review-plan -> PASS (0 blocking). Added: security_iac_public_exposure.yaml (0.0.0.0/0, ::/0, associate_public_ip_address, internet-facing aws_lb, non-loopback compose bind; tfsec/Checkov-cited; FP guards as pattern exclusions). engine_b._LANG_EXTENSIONS gains terraform/hcl/yaml. New advisory DET criterion public-exposure-without-auth (blocking_enabled:false, fail_mode:open) under a dedicated rebar.builtin.iac.public-exposure. prefix (not the fail-closed security prefix). ADR 0019 records the design. Tests pass with real semgrep: 5 positives match, private-CIDR/loopback/internal-LB negatives don't, and a match stays advisory (verdict PASS). make lint green."},"env_id":"ade0f2ef-51cc-45a2-bb97-c09846cd3df5","event_type":"COMMENT","timestamp":1782934028603066001,"uuid":"0acf9cf8-f729-4beb-b9b2-22fc4356303c"}